{"tid":2166744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭文貴及前白宮資深顧問班農有關係的媒體公司遭到聯邦與州政府雙重調查","createTime":"2020-08-20T15:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T07:16:09.000Z","uid":198088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"67a8442a60c5fd0c0176cb2db9b444eb7421997a","tid":2166744,"uid":198088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:15:11.000Z","msg":"前任白宮資深顧問巴農(Steve Bannon)涉嫌侵占高達2500萬元的「我們來築牆」(We Build the Wall)募款，將民眾募款挪為私用，20日早晨被捕並遭到密謀電匯詐騙、密謀洗錢等罪名起訴。巴農20日稍後將首次出庭。另一方面，華爾街日報報導，消息人士透露，與流亡中國富商郭文貴(Guo Wengui)及巴農都有關係的媒體公司，今春募得3億多元私人資金，如今也遭到聯邦與州政府的雙重調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/7107295/article-%E5%89%8D%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E5%B7%B4%E8%BE%B2-%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%A7%E4%BE%B5%E5%8D%A02500%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E7%AF%89%E7%89%86%E5%8B%9F%E6%AC%BE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/?ref=%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F7107295%2Farticle-%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25BE%25B2-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E5%258D%25A02500%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%25AF%2589%25E7%2589%2586%25E5%258B%259F%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F%3Fref%3D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5TBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=ba374b78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/7107295/article-%E5%89%8D%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E5%B7%B4%E8%BE%B2-%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%A7%E4%BE%B5%E5%8D%A02500%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E7%AF%89%E7%89%86%E5%8B%9F%E6%AC%BE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/?ref=%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E</a>"},{"pid":"8acc76bafab91e7264db3131d5fa757bc345a8fe","tid":2166744,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=